---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lastUpdated = 'May 1, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Apron Belly Guide"
  description="Privacy Policy for Apron Belly Guide. How we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-10">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="prose prose-stone max-w-none prose-headings:font-sans prose-a:text-sage-green prose-a:no-underline hover:prose-a:underline">

      <p>Apron Belly Guide ("we," "us," or "our") operates apronbellyguide.com. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our site.</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

      <h3>Information you provide</h3>
      <p>If you subscribe to our email list or contact us, we collect the information you submit (name, email address). We do not sell this information to third parties.</p>

      <h3>Automatically collected information</h3>
      <p>Like most websites, we may collect standard log data including your IP address, browser type, pages visited, and referral source. This data is used in aggregate to understand how visitors use the site.</p>

      <h3>Cookies</h3>
      <p>We use cookies and similar tracking technologies for analytics and to enable affiliate link tracking. You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect site functionality.</p>

      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To deliver content and respond to inquiries</li>
        <li>To send email newsletters if you have subscribed (you can unsubscribe at any time)</li>
        <li>To analyze site traffic and improve our content</li>
        <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Affiliate Disclosure & Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>Apron Belly Guide participates in affiliate advertising programs including Amazon Associates, ShareASale, CJ Affiliate, and Impact. When you click an affiliate link and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. Affiliate relationships do not influence our editorial recommendations.</p>
      <p>Our site contains links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of those sites.</p>

      <h2>Analytics</h2>
      <p>We may use third-party analytics services (such as Google Analytics) to understand site usage. These services may collect information about your visits using cookies and similar technologies. You can opt out of Google Analytics by installing the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.</p>

      <h2>Email Marketing</h2>
      <p>If you subscribe to our email list, your email address is stored with our email service provider. You can unsubscribe at any time using the link in any email we send. We do not share email subscriber lists with third parties.</p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>Our site is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your personal data, including the right to access, correct, or delete the information we hold about you. To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@apronbellyguide.com">contact@apronbellyguide.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page reflects when changes were last made.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this Privacy Policy? Email us at <a href="mailto:contact@apronbellyguide.com">contact@apronbellyguide.com</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
